reviewText: I love this series,...beware though...you can buy the 4 separate seasons separately for less than this bundle.
A nice way to unwind and laugh.
I gave it two stars because it sounds like a good idea but it is actually cheaper to buy them separately.
Love the show!  I was watching on Amazon Prime, but was unable to watch all before the free viewing was taken away.  It was cheaper to get the bundle than buy streaming from Amazon.
